Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:21.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}全身に　光をあつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.24,0:01:21.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让全身充满光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:23.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}どこに　あるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.27,0:01:23.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}告訴我在哪裡
